SketchController is a program that uses an external gamepad to simulate the effect of an Etch-A-Sketch. Spinning the joysticks on the controller will move your cursor either horizontally or vertically. The right shoulder button is left click, and the left shoulder button is right click.

To exit the program at any time, press the guide button on your controller.

Dependencies:
	libsdl2-dev
	libx11-dev
	libxtst-dev
	libc6-dev
